OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCourts to stop allowing    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fforced meter installations 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Magistrates courts in England and Wales
OL,6, have been ordered to stop authorising  
OL,7, warrants for energy firms to forcibly  
OL,8, install prepayment meters with         
OL,9, immediate effect.                      
OL,11,FOne of the country's most senior judges
OL,12,Fsaid the cases must be halted in light 
OL,13,Fof the growing concern.                
OL,15,FIt comes days after the BBC revealed   
OL,16,Fthat courts have been waving through   
OL,17,Fapplications to install these meters.  
OL,19,FRegulator Ofgem has asked all companies
OL,20,Fto suspend forcible installations.     
